  "text": "The Transition does not take effect when using conditional judgment on the diff element in the render function.\n\n### Vue version\r\n\r\n3.3.8\r\n\r\n### Link to minimal reproduction\r\n\r\nhttps://play.vuejs.org/#\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/vuejs/core/assets/41265413/a69ed32a-d955-4316-be6e-f472bbcc5992\r\n\r\n\r\n### Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\n1. click toggle button\r\n2. The one above didn't work. The one below, written with sfc, works.\r\n\r\n### What is expected?\r\n\r\n1. all should works\r\n\r\n### What is actually happening?\r\n\r\n1. component written in render function not working\r\n\r\n### System Info\r\n\r\n_No response_\r\n\r\n### Any additional comments?\r\n\r\n_No response_",
